    },
    "The toggle should turn **green** when enabled" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Der Schalter sollte **grün** werden, wenn aktiviert"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This step is optional for using this app, but required to send prints over LAN." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dieser Schritt ist optional für die App-Nutzung, aber nötig, um Drucke über LAN zu senden."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To send prints over LAN, you'll also need to update your slicer's connection settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um Drucke über LAN zu senden, musst du auch die Verbindungseinstellungen deines Slicers aktualisieren."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "View on Bambu Wiki" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Im Bambu Wiki ansehen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Welcome to PandaBeFree" : {
      "comment" : "The welcome message at the top of the onboarding screen.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Willkommen bei PandaBeFree"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "With LAN Mode enabled, scroll down in **Settings**" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Scrolle mit aktiviertem LAN Mode in den **Einstellungen** nach unten"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can change notification preferences anytime in **More > Notifications**." : {
      "comment" : "Text describing where the user can change their notification preferences.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "You'll need your printer's IP address and access code to connect. Some printer models might also require the serial number." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du brauchst die IP-Adresse und den Zugangscode deines Druckers. Einige Druckermodelle benötigen zusätzlich die Seriennummer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your iPhone must be on the same network as your printer (LAN mode only). Using a VPN like Tailscale or WireGuard is the easiest way to connect remotely." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dein iPhone muss im selben Netzwerk wie dein Drucker sein (nur LAN Mode). Ein VPN wie Tailscale oder WireGuard ist die einfachste Möglichkeit für den Fernzugriff."
          }
        }
      }
    }
